{"tid":976267,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加州大學籲師生在中國避用微信WhatsApp 「可能遭罰不准出境」","createTime":"2019-01-10T09:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T11:23:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d70206bdfc02a433aa5286b5a50879e1f4ef34","tid":976267,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190110/large/1547108419_3846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190110%2Flarge%2F1547108419_3846.jpg&h=a64fc0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加州大學戴維斯分校（UC Davis）近日向全校師生發出電郵，建議到中國旅遊期間不要使用WhatsApp或微信（WeChat）等即時通訊軟件。<br />\n<br />\n網民「瘋狂科學魚博士」8日在twitter轉發這封電郵，內容是校方提出在華旅行需要有7項注意，包括不得隨便拍照；妥善保管護照，除非遇到暴力威脅，不要隨便交出護照；保護個人資料；保持電話暢通；不要在社交媒體發表「不利的政治聲明或網帖」。<br />\n<br />\n電郵中還暗示中國政府會「扣留」美國赴華旅行公民，並引用俄羅斯的個案：「雖然在中國用WhatsApp或者微信是合法，我們擔心的是，由於此前俄羅斯在審訊美國間諜時曾指控他使用WhatsApp，中國可能效仿俄羅斯一樣對西方旅客進行處罰，或者以此為藉口拒絕西方旅客出境。我們建議現在不要使用這些應用程式。」<br />\n<br />\n該校表明電郵並非校方正式通告，只是私下由「校長信箱」直接發給理工系學生，並強調這些警告來自一間私人的情報公司，並非代表校方立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190110/59127242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59127242&d=5hU%2Bn4bYNeSznHwm6AP4zMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=a99d93ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190110%2F59127242&h=872926bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190110/59127242</a>"},{"pid":"3b405f54b279f6a3752e190e36e6ba2af3f91f37","tid":976267,"uid":29702,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T10:12:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fd4aa9a48bec95b02fbc0fbc275f33737380b16","tid":976267,"uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"3b405f54b279f6a3752e190e36e6ba2af3f91